該大學共有四個學院，有近40個主專業和近40個輔修專業<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.transy.edu/pages/regidis/1415/patterns.htm?mi=catalog|title = Academic Majors, Minors, and Preprofessional Studies|date = January 16, 2015|accessdate = |website = Transylvania University|publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2016-01-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160108012224/http://www.transy.edu/pages/regidis/1415/patterns.htm?mi=catalog|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.transy.edu/about/facts.htm|title = Quick Facts|date = January 16, 2015|accessdate = |website = Transylvania University|publisher = |last = |first = |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160323012806/http://www2.transy.edu/about/facts.htm|archive-date = 2016-03-23|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>[http://www.transy.edu/academics/majors_minors.htm#self Self-designed Majors and Minors.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.transy.edu/academics/majors_minors.htm |date=20160314023405 }}  University publication. Retrieved August 26, 2012.</ref>。

